### 1. 正常查询：从 1 号站到 5 号站
# @name 正常查询
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tickets/query?fromStationId=1&toStationId=5
Accept: application/json

### 2. 参数缺失测试：缺少 toStationId (应返回 400 Bad Request)
# @name 缺失参数测试
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tickets/query?fromStationId=1
Accept: application/json

### 3. 空结果测试：查询一个数据库里没有的区间 (应返回 204 No Content)
# @name 无结果测试
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tickets/query?fromStationId=999&toStationId=888
Accept: application/json

### 4. 复杂区间测试：例如从 2 号站到 10 号站
# @name 跨度查询
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tickets/query?fromStationId=1&toStationId=3
Accept: application/json

###############################################
# 初始化相关测试
###############################################

### 5. 初始化单个车次的指定座位类型
# @name 初始化单个车次单个座位类型
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tickets/initialize?trainId=1100&seatType=1
Accept: application/json

### 6. 初始化单个车次的所有座位类型
# @name 初始化单个车次所有座位类型
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tickets/initialize?trainId=1001
Accept: application/json

### 7. 批量初始化车次（1001-1010）
# @name 批量初始化
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tickets/initialize/batch?startTrainId=1001&endTrainId=1100
Accept: application/json

### 8. 查询车次剩余配额
# @name 查询配额
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tickets/quota?trainId=1100
Accept: application/json

###############################################
# 抢票相关测试
###############################################

### 9. 正常抢票请求（二等座）
# @name 正常抢票
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tickets/book
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

userId=8888&trainId=1100&fromIndex=1&toIndex=3&seatType=2

### 10. 正常抢票请求（一等座）
# @name 抢票一等座
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tickets/book
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

userId=8889&trainId=1001&fromIndex=0&toIndex=1&seatType=1

### 11. 跨站抢票（长途）
# @name 跨站抢票
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tickets/book
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

userId=8890&trainId=1001&fromIndex=0&toIndex=9&seatType=2

### 12. 短途抢票
# @name 短途抢票
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tickets/book
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

userId=8891&trainId=1003&fromIndex=3&toIndex=4&seatType=2

### 13. 不同车次抢票
# @name 不同车次
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tickets/book
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

userId=8892&trainId=1002&fromIndex=1&toIndex=5&seatType=2

